race.comment: PIERATA'S GEM (5) resumes for a hot yard and looks well placed. Spent all last campaign in richer company over the winter carnival including a couple of stakes races and won a Quality at Eagle Farm. Fitter for two trials and looks primed to go close. DIRTY DANCING (2) has the fitness edge and looks close to a win. Has placed the last two, beaten neck fresh at Eagle Farm then a length here latest. Should go close again. SUJEED (9) has been freshened since running below par last time in richer company. Best form stacks up and is worth another chance.  MAJESTIC BOOM (3) looks well placed here. Fitter for three trials and the trip suits. Is a soft track winner and drawn for a good run.
